Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:15.56,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,This is Kyou, my elder daughte{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.86,0:00:19.66,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,She’s fifteen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:28.24,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,This one is Asu, my younger daughte{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:30.24,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,She’s only nine years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.29,0:00:38.36,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,To ensure that she doesn’t wake her siste{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}, Kyou\Nalways gets up quickly when the alarm clock rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.72,0:00:51.53,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Every morning, Kyou leaves to deliver newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:00:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’ll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.68,0:00:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.99,0:01:06.58,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Asu. I can’t wait for today’s fireworks festival!{festival?}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.10,0:01:16.16,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I’ve always been watching over\Nthe two of them from heaven.{this is hella clunk}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.71,0:01:22.97,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I was able to leave behind just\None thing for the two of you:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.04,0:01:26.75,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}a small promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom went to heaven the year Asu was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.57,0:01:49.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad disappeared after accumulating gambling debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.41,0:01:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thus, we were abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:58.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a 40-year-old, one-room,\Ndilapidated apartment with no bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:00.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.34,0:02:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, when spring comes…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! Onee-chan will be getting home soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:58.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to start preparing breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m finally done.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.51,0:04:14.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, last yea{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}, Asu was the one who really looked forward to the fireworks festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this yea{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:29.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That’s right! The change from yesterday’s grocery shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m counting on you. I’ve saved up little by little just for this da{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan and I are going to have a lot of fun at the food stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Candy apples,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,takoyaki,{melody capitalizes this, wry?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:50.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and rice crackers with sauce.{“senbei” a specific type of Japanese rice crackers, but doremi just goes with: “Japanese crackers”}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:00.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Breakfast is read{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:04.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today’s the day of the fireworks festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:14.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, after I finish cleaning, may I go out for a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:22.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That’s fine. It is Sunda{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:23.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You’ll find out late{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:35.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next-door neighbo{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}, your mailbox is full!{yeah, no, it still sounds retarded, but I won’t stand for “neighbor-san”, better suggestions desired}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s really full!{don’t shout too loudly now, Asu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:43.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu! Be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, seriousl{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You’ll find out late{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, M{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}. Landlord, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:57.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!{orig: All right!}{my translation: “hai!”}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:33.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn’t Asu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, it’s Yaoichi’s husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going to be selling vegetables at this stand today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vegetables wouldn’t sell too well at a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:43.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! These are…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:46.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we’re going to be a candy apple stand toda{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? A candy apple stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:52.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My sister and I will come by later to buy one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:55.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay! Then I’ll prepare an extra large one just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.61,0:07:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There’s the yakisoba stand, the shooting game stand, and the cotton candy stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:14.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s done{complete}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ma’am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:44.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-The money is…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu, I’m home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:08:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry I’m so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:03.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong? The lights aren’t even on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, Asu, it’s a present.
