Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where’d you get this?{orig: Why do you have this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bought it at the Hashimoto clothing store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:26.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have Mom’s hand-me-down yukata, but you don’t have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:29.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’ve been wanting to get you one as a present for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don’t tell me… You used the money in the piggy bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:36.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That’s right. Hurry up and try it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:44.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don’t want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:48.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why? I bought this for you, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:52.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you spend the money by yourself?{on y’own}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, “why”? I thought you’d like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:09:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, we can always save the money back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oka{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, it’s my fault for spending the money without asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since the day’s here, put on your new yukata\Nand we’ll go to the fireworks festival, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.43,0:09:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who cares about the fireworks festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m not going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:19.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:31.47,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I saved that money for so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:34.24,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,just so we could spend it together at the fireworks festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:38.14,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,The takoyaki stand. The rice cracker stand, too…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:41.35,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Everything that I was waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:45.26,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I really wanted us to eat a big candy apple together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m going to return this yukata.
